## Phase 1 — Project Bootstrap

### 1.1 Initialize Expo App
```bash
cd budgetcap
npx create-expo-app@latest mobile --template blank-typescript
cd mobile
```

### 1.2 Install Core Dependencies
```bash
# Navigation
npx expo install expo-router expo-status-bar expo-constants expo-linking expo-system-ui

# NativeWind v4 + Tailwind
npm install nativewind tailwindcss
npm install --save-dev tailwindcss@3

# State & Data Fetching
npm install @tanstack/react-query zustand

# Auth / Storage
npx expo install expo-secure-store

# UI Utilities
npx expo install expo-haptics expo-image react-native-reanimated react-native-gesture-handler react-native-safe-area-context react-native-screens

# Charts (Reports screen)
npm install victory-native@next react-native-svg
```

### 1.3 Configure NativeWind v4
```js
// tailwind.config.js
module.exports = {
  content: ["./app/**/*.{ts,tsx}", "./components/**/*.{ts,tsx}"],
  presets: [require("nativewind/preset")],
  theme: {
    extend: {
      colors: {
        primary: { DEFAULT: "#6366f1", dark: "#4f46e5" },
        surface: { DEFAULT: "#1e1e2e", card: "#2a2a3e" },
        // ... mirror web CSS variables
      },
    },
  },
};
```

### 1.4 Configure Expo Router
```json
// app.json
{
  "expo": {
    "scheme": "budgetcap",
    "plugins": ["expo-router"]
  }
}
```

