## Phase 4 — Screen Implementation

### 4.1 Dashboard / Budget Tab (`index.tsx`)

**Web equivalent:** `/budget` page

| Element | Native Implementation |
|---------|----------------------|
| Month selector | Horizontal `FlatList` of month chips, swipe gesture |
| "To Budget" bar | Custom animated progress bar with `Animated.Value` |
| Envelope Set accordion | `SectionList` with animated expand/collapse |
| Envelope row | Swipeable row (gesture handler) → quick-edit on swipe |
| Add Allocation FAB | `TouchableOpacity` floating button → bottom sheet |

**Data:** `GET /api/envelopes?month=X&year=Y&householdId=Z`

### 4.2 Transactions Tab (`transactions.tsx`)

**Web equivalent:** `/transactions` page

| Element | Native Implementation |
|---------|----------------------|
| Filter bar | Horizontal pill filter (All / Income / Expense / Transfer) |
| Transaction list | `FlashList` (high-perf) grouped by date |
| Add Transaction | FAB → `BottomSheet` with full form |
| Search | `SearchBar` component, filters local list |
| Swipe to delete | `react-native-gesture-handler` swipeable |

**Data:** `GET /api/transactions?householdId=Z&limit=50&offset=0`

### 4.3 Accounts Tab (`accounts.tsx`)

**Web equivalent:** `/accounts` page

| Element | Native Implementation |
|---------|----------------------|
| Account cards | Styled `FlatList` cards (Checking, Savings, Cash) |
| Balance display | Large number with formatted paise → rupee |
| Add Account | Bottom sheet form |

### 4.4 Reports Tab (`reports.tsx`)

**Web equivalent:** `/reports` page

| Element | Native Implementation |
|---------|----------------------|
| Spending by envelope | Pie chart (`victory-native`) |
| Monthly trend | Bar chart |
| Date range picker | Custom month-range picker |

### 4.5 Envelope Detail (`envelope/[id].tsx`)

- Envelope name, goal progress ring (if `isGoal`)
- Current month allocation + spent + available
- Transaction history filtered to envelope
- Edit allocation inline

### 4.6 Settings (`settings/index.tsx`)

- Profile (name, email, change password)
- Household management
- Envelope set management → `/settings/envelopes`
- Theme toggle (dark/light)
- Logout

