Build mobile-native equivalents of the web shadcn components:

| Web Component | Mobile Component | Notes |
|--------------|-----------------|-------|
| `<Button>` | `<Button>` | Pressable + haptic feedback |
| `<Input>` | `<TextInput>` wrapper | Floating label animation |
| `<Dialog>` | `<BottomSheet>` | Full-screen modal or half sheet |
| `<Select>` | `<Picker>` / ActionSheet | iOS / Android native |
| `<Badge>` | `<Badge>` | Pill with color variants |
| `<Card>` | `<Card>` | Elevated surface with shadow |
| `<Separator>` | `<View style border>` | Simple HR |
| `<Toast>` | `react-native-toast-message` | Global toast provider |

All components styled with **NativeWind** class strings.

